{"title":"船厂节日","authors":["宁宇"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":4,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"船厂节日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个工业之子将诞生——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一艘新船要下水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅呵，眼迷乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望上一眼心儿醉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄浦江春潮来迎接，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横空的彩旗拍云飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓点如雨浪花跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血在燃烧手不累……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅的妻子在产院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头胎怀子喜在心田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新船下水锣鼓喧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宛如心愿频频催。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣鼓声中婴儿落地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸伸胳膊蹬蹬腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顿时笑声展翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕着船台码头飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅惊喜斧一闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船似飞箭射下水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溅起满江雪浪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溶进无数欢喜泪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天彩霞汽笛鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南北海港伸手臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为祖国，为母亲，为孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我们建设的生活呼万岁！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}